This toolkit contains a curated extraction of image-matching code adapted from:

  AirtestProject / Airtest
  https://github.com/AirtestProject/Airtest
  Apache License 2.0
  Extracted from commit d729c631d2032521be1e2168a249a2a89d79af2a

Included and adapted areas:
- airtest/aircv/aircv.py
- airtest/aircv/cal_confidence.py
- airtest/aircv/error.py
- airtest/aircv/template.py
- airtest/aircv/multiscale_template_matching.py
- airtest/aircv/utils.py
- airtest/utils/logger.py

Changes made in this repo:
- Repackaged into a smaller module surface for asset workflows only
- Removed device automation dependencies
- Added JSON CLI commands for `match`, `scan-dir`, `compare`, and `doctor`
- Added repo-aware path handling and annotated preview export
- Reduced dependency scope to the subset needed for asset matching
